  "text": "Molecular docking results were then visualized using Discovery Studio 4.1, LigPlot + and LigandScout 3.1 softwares [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Analysis of interactions between protein and ligand was made to see the number and type of chemical bonds formed.",
